{"tid":2318280,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實本地抗爭係咪已經完成歷史任務？！香港人係咪已經盡左力？！","createTime":"2020-12-09T08:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T08:57:24.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e0cacd93a302729e2f7c92601d4a41c347b58758","tid":2318280,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:29:07.000Z","msg":"只從抗爭角度，不談個人得失。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本地抗爭係咪真係只受到所謂疫情影響？ 疫情後（2021-2022）香港人係咪會突破恐懼關口再次抗爭，定係還是已經走夾唔唞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我心中一早已經有答案，連登仔又點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> - 香港未死，忍一忍重燃抗爭之火<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> - 2019港人已盡力，無悔地離開"},{"pid":"d468778aa7fd7dac6d10502ff805be1911b7280e","tid":2318280,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5ca0a0cd0046f8b03dacc8fcd473c51d81b07d","tid":2318280,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:35:24.000Z","msg":"成功或失敗，呢個問題唔係由一開始就明明可知咩？"},{"pid":"64838d620fc6652d4966332ca17621f2af438f3c","tid":2318280,"uid":276839,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:49:58.000Z","msg":"冇基層出黎打交賣命抗閪咩。 靠啲白鴿眼用把口反，食屎啦。有得比你走就走啦，重要扮抗爭。"},{"pid":"f6d6cf4e53f711342d51af01f45014d575f189d6","tid":2318280,"uid":383130,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:50:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef0847a81c10a24fc4cfda6a04ce142eb210d24f","tid":2318280,"uid":345137,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:57:03.000Z","msg":"吓, 而家走先係抗爭wo. <br />\n出來抗爭既目的係令對家統治成本高, 降低對家收入同提升支出, 斷其水路<br />\n一個中產走左, 香港唔見幾千萬, 現階段係低成本高效益<br />\n說服10個中產走, 對共產黨傷害仲大過打死一堆黑警"},{"pid":"9adb26b09440cb89d6dd5bb4b81ccdf08d35ee97","tid":2318280,"uid":174607,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:57:24.000Z","msg":"走同唔走都一樣可以抗爭<br />\n同埋要贏支共一定唔係靠街頭抗爭"}]}